text: Keddie is a census-designated place in Plumas County, California, United States. The population was 51 at the 2020 census. Keddie is located at (40.005901, -120.956899). Keddie was also the site of the Keddie murders, a notorious quadruple homicide. == References == Category:Census-designated places in California Category:Settlements in Plumas County, California
title: Keddie, California
